<P align=center><B><FONT size=5>Alternate Site Games&nbsp;Since 2001</FONT></B></P>
<P>This list shows games played <font color="#FF0000">since 2001</font> by major league clubs in a ballpark and/or city 
that is not home to either team. There have been many reasons that these games 
have been moved through the years such as Sunday Blue Laws, park capacity and 
fires. Most of these games are between teams in the same league but a few of the 
more recent contests are interleague.</P>
<P>This data was compiled by David Vincent and others from many different sources. If you 
find an error or have data to add, please contact the webmaster.
</P>
<P>To see the 19th century games, <a href="neutral19.htm">click here</a>.<br>
To see the 20th century games, <a href="neutral20.htm">click here</a>.</P>
<p>Additions, changes (for older years):<BR>
11/22/2020: 1901-2000 split off into its own page</p>

